article_title: The problem with a ticker-tape parade for New York's Covid heroes (opinion)
meta_description: A collective salute to our essential workers is well deserved and likely even cathartic, writes Jill Filipovic. But it's not enough for so many of these workers who can't afford to even live in this city. How about well-paying jobs, expanded affordable housing and universal child care as more genuine expressions of support.  And how about the city taking meaningful steps to ensure widespread vaccinations and reasonable masking to ensure that workers' sacrifice was not for naught.
